CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "Paper Counter (Filing Department) - Ralph W. Johnson, clerk (kneeling), and Fred Schwartz, clerk."
TitMainTitle: Clerks Ralph W. Johnson, kneeling, and Fred Schwartz, examining files in large file storage room of Allegheny County Prothonotray office
